Most viral, wow thanks! If anyone is interested in following us dating each other at Disney, I’ve recently started an Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/disney.dating.couple/</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/tJ0kDIR.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Now lunch at Raglan Road, having my first drink in almost a year. Little scary!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/DCBptFm.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Suggested by the barkeep. Pretty tasty. A little sweet, which was my goal.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/OMAGRdf</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[learntorv]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>TIL</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/Nrfic68</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/tOQhnLi.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Nrfic68</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Srajo101]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>An important PSA (sound on)</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/LhsRQbp</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/MYU19bC.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I'm considered tall for a lady, but my husband is my same height and I love it. Don't be shy short fellas! By the way Her name is Grace Hayes and here's her youtube channel. https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCARvd_Xh2rBrM8yEAp9JdMQ</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/LhsRQbp</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[noproblllama]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>To be fair it is one kind of tie!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/Mdk7AhT</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/NEIoro2.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I’m the only teacher in my building who always wears a tie. Professional ties, Garcia ties, cartoon ties, old ties (as in 1970-80s hand-me-downs), funky ties, ugly ties,…and well, you get the picture. I own over 130 ties. Almost all of them given to me. I believe I’ve paid for four.

Well, there is one tie I wear that my students look for every day, a solid black tie. I only wear them on test days. The reasoning I tell my students a test is as professional as a Black Tie Affair. Whenever a student sees me with a black tie on and it is not for their class their eyes get big and ask panically, “DO WE HAVE A TEST?” I have now classically conditioned them to fear my ties.

As a side note, we have finals. I also dress up for that. I’ve gone to the GoodWill and got a tuxedo. So on finals I wear that and my students laugh at it.

TL;DR I wear black ties on test days and my kids are afraid of them now.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/YRY0xuc.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Proof of my collection!</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Mdk7AhT</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Hotsauceman]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Being nice to people is free. There's so much hate on this earth. Gotta look after your fellow man</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/4sc3IWf</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/iq6hWzF.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/4sc3IWf</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Srajo101]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Macron wins will 58% of the votes but this is what fighting a racist at the poll should look like.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/HqeirRe</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/qy46O0w.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>For the non french people of Imgur, JM Le Pen is Marine Le Pen's dad, their party was renamed a few years ago (to try to rebrand it) but is still fascist and racist.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/HqeirRe</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Spamoi]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Love it</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/dNsgMh0</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/YQK5Djh.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/TkUCcG7.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Qznm8yt.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/19waJYA.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.img