EDIT 2: Guys! (And gals/ghouls/gremlins) I said I wanted to vent to Usersub! But you assholes banded together to get me to Most Viral. Thank you. ?
My mother died of cancer when I was 3. Dad struggled to provide for all of us younger kids. He hated “assistance” and fought hard to not be on it. So he was unable to save. As of December, I was promoted and I now make more than my siblings. I have no spouse, no kids, and no mortgage. I owe him as much to give him a wonderful resting place when he couldn’t do so for mom. 
I don’t want bragging rights over him. I just know if he could, he’d have sold anything to bury me. He’s the only parent I remembered. 

EDIT: He just passed. I’m thankful he’s no longer in pain. Im going to go somewhere he’d love and toast my coffee to his memory. 

I just need to vent into the Usersub void. 

I’m the youngest of what was at one point nine kids. We are familiar with death and the funeral home is a familiar place, but I knew this would hit different. I’m planning on paying the $12k bill myself since my two oldest siblings are greedy and would hold it over everyone’s heads until they pass. 

Plus I knew my oldest sister would claim the $10k burial fund we all agreed to set aside from the sale of our grandmother’s house was spent paying the taxes and repairs on dad’s shithole house. A house that honestly should have been condemned since 2005. 

To be honest, I want to disappear from my family for a long while after dad passes. I know at least the two oldest will fight over his possessions. I’m washing my hands of them for a while. 

His slow decline is breaking me and I’ve told him today he doesn’t have to fight anymore.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/SymsV66</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Schmaron]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Look at this distguished gentleman</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/awRtiyX</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/aLbdq6H.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Sawyer is one of the goodest boys</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/tHCylYN.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>And here he is with his favorite teddy bear</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/awRtiyX</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[PipeandSlippers]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Ikr</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/dqYM3sc</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/YnH330B.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/dqYM3sc</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[mfrybeasley]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>teenage father.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/POzeC5T</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/JK5lIRt.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/POzeC5T</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[arhamXD]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>yes</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/5YkrnHl</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/3U6jgpV.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/5YkrnHl</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[fulcrims]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Self inflicted dementia.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/OUCll2P</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/LuA8UX8.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height